description._content: Collection: NASA Johnson Space Center Collection Title: Space suit A-3H-024 with Lunar Excursion Module astronaut restraint harness Description: Engineer Bill Peterson fits test pilot Bob Smyth in space suit A-3H-024 with the Lunar Excursion Module astronaut restraint harness during suit evaluation study.
